<BaseLayout title="How to Protect Your Content From AI Scraping | Technical & Legal Guide" description="A complete guide to stopping AI bots from scraping your website content. Learn how to use robots.txt, meta tags, and legal strategies to protect your IP.">
  <article class="acl-article">
    <header class="acl-article-header">
      <div class="acl-container">
        <nav aria-label="Breadcrumb" class="acl-breadcrumb">
